- UH, WELL, UM--

00:00:35.169 --> 00:00:36.303
- WAIT,
IS YOUR BURGER THE BEST?

00:00:36.336 --> 00:00:38.105
- OF COURSE,
IT'S THE BEST.

00:00:38.138 --> 00:00:41.341
- 'CAUSE NO BURGER PLACE
HAS EVER MADE A CLAIM LIKE THIS,

00:00:41.375 --> 00:00:46.113
BUT YOU CAN,
'CAUSE YOU'RE THE BEST.

