- GUSTAVO AGREED TO PUT UP
HIS OWN CASH FOR THE PROMOTION,

00:00:53.420 --> 00:00:54.855
AND IT WAS
SUCH AN AMAZING OFFER,

00:00:54.888 --> 00:00:56.690
THAT I WAS EASILY ABLE
TO LAND US

00:00:56.723 --> 00:00:59.393
