IT'S GONNA BE $100 BILL.

00:01:07.334 --> 00:01:08.769
- WOW, THAT'S IMPRESSIVE.
- THAT'S--

00:01:08.802 --> 00:01:09.870
THAT'S A LOT OF BALLS,
GUSTAVO...

00:01:09.903 --> 00:01:11.572
- YEAH.
- 100 BUCKS, 'CAUSE I MEAN,

00:01:11.605 --> 00:01:13.307
AREN'T YOU--I MEAN,
